      listOfForums: [{&#34;id&#34;:29184736,&#34;userId&#34;:3445367,&#34;url&#34;:&#34;amcc-basic-general-rule&#34;,&#34;body&#34;:&#34;&lt;p&gt;Chess + Anime Club &amp;ndash; Updated Jan 31, 2026&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Respect No harassment, slurs, toxicity, or personal attacks. Keep banter friendly. Respect boundaries.&lt;br \/&gt;Fair Play Zero cheating (engines, smurfs, sandbagging). Violations = review &amp;rarr; warning &amp;rarr; ban. Obvious cases = instant ban.&lt;br \/&gt;Chat English main. Mild swearing OK. NSFW in marked channels only. No spam, copypasta, or disruption.&lt;\/p&gt;&#34;,&#34;isLocked&#34;:1,&#34;isSticky&#34;:1,&#34;subject&#34;:&#34;Anime Team Club Rules&#34;,&#34;createDate&#34;:&#34;2016-05-31 15:47:13&#34;,&#34;postCount&#34;:1,&#34;viewCount&#34;:360,&#34;languageId&#34;:10,&#34;lastForumTopicId&#34;:29184736,&#34;lastForumTopicCreateDate&#34;:&#34;2016-05-31 15:47:13&#34;,&#34;lastUserId&#34;:3445367,&#34;topicUserId&#34;:3445367,&#34;bodyButtonSet&#34;:null,&#34;create_timestamp&#34;:1464734833,&#34;topicUsername&#34;:&#34;SageMode&#34;,&#34;lastPostUserId&#34;:3445367,&#34;lastPostUsername&#34;:&#34;SageMode&#34;,&#34;lastPostMembershipLevel&#34;:10,&#34;authorChessTitle&#34;:null,&#34;lastPostUserIsEnabled&#34;:true,&#34;lastPostUserIsContentHidden&#34;:false,&#34;lastPostUserUuid&#34;:&#34;e6f546d2-7f13-11df-8043-000000000000&#34;,&#34;lastPostMainImageHash&#34;:&#34;132cea5f&#34;,&#34;lastPostMainImageExtension&#34;:&#34;jpeg&#34;,&#34;status&#34;:&#34;locked&#34;,&#34;lastPostMainImage&#34;:&#34;https:\/\/images.chesscomfiles.com\/uploads\/v1\/user\/3445367.132cea5f.40x40o.234d691a0bed.jpeg&#34;},{&#34;id&#34;:29006020,&#34;userId&#34;:1802156,&#34;url&#34;:&#34;a-mcc-puzzle-corner-ii&#34;,&#34;body&#34;:&#34;&lt;p&gt;Hello everyone!&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\u00a0&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;As promised, here&#39;s the return of this space that our group used to have in the past.&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\u00a0&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;To make this more organized and effective, i will ask for those who post a puzzle &lt;strong&gt;to indicate before the puzzle\u00a0what kind of themes are present + indicate how difficult it is (using *, with 1* being very easy, and 5* being very hard)&lt;\/strong&gt;. If possible, post more than 1 puzzle about the same theme, its makes easier for people to start assimilating the ideas for their game.&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;A short introduction, describing the position strenghts and weaknesses is also welcome, although this is optional.&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\u00a0&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\u00a0&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;To start with, i will post here some examples about &lt;strong&gt;\&#34;Double Attacks\&#34;&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\u00a0&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1*&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;div style=\&#34;text-align:center;\&#34;&gt;\n&lt;!-- CHESS_COM_DIAGRAM &lt;div style=\&#34;text-align:center;\&#34;&gt; --&gt;&lt;div id=\&#34;chess_com_diagram_1_3005194\&#34; class=\&#34;chessDiagramDiv\&#34; align=\&#34;center\&#34; style=\&#34;clear:both;\&#34;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;div style=\&#34;text-align:center;\&#34;&gt;\u00a0&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;div style=\&#34;text-align:left;\&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2* &lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;div style=\&#34;text-align:left;\&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;This is a famous mistake by one of the most famous chess world champions. Playing Christiansen with black, Karpov missed a really simple tactic in the opening...&lt;\/em&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;\n&lt;!-- CHESS_COM_DIAGRAM &lt;div style=\&#34;text-align:center;\&#34;&gt; --&gt;&lt;div id=\&#34;chess_com_diagram_2_3005204\&#34; class=\&#34;chessDiagramDiv\&#34; align=\&#34;center\&#34; style=\&#34;clear:both;\&#34;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;div style=\&#34;text-align:center;\&#34;&gt;\u00a0&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;div style=\&#34;text-align:left;\&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3*&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;div style=\&#34;text-align:left;\&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Offering a trade when leaving pieces unprotected can turn into disaster...&lt;\/em&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;div style=\&#34;text-align:left;\&#34;&gt;\u00a0&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;div style=\&#34;text-align:left;\&#34;&gt;\n&lt;!-- CHESS_COM_DIAGRAM &lt;div style=\&#34;text-align:center;\&#34;&gt; --&gt;&lt;div id=\&#34;chess_com_diagram_3_3005214\&#34; class=\&#34;chessDiagramDiv\&#34; align=\&#34;center\&#34; style=\&#34;clear:both;\&#34;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;div style=\&#34;text-align:center;\&#34;&gt;\u00a0&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4*&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;em&gt;This is a typical chaotic position. Both kings are in a dire situation, with major pieces active all over the board. White has the turn, so must use that to his advantage.&lt;\/em&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;\u00a0&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;\n&lt;div style=\&#34;text-align:center;\&#34;&gt;\n&lt;!-- CHESS_COM_DIAGRAM &lt;div style=\&#34;text-align:center;\&#34;&gt; --&gt;&lt;div id=\&#34;chess_com_diagram_4_3005244\&#34; class=\&#34;chessDiagramDiv\&#34; align=\&#34;center\&#34; style=\&#34;clear:both;\&#34;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;\/div&gt;&#34;,&#34;isLocked&#34;:0,&#34;isSticky&#34;:1,&#34;subject&#34;:&#34;A&amp;MCC Puzzle Corner II&#34;,&#34;createDate&#34;:&#34;2016-05-15 10:29:03&#34;,&#34;postCount&#34;:14,&#34;viewCount&#34;:516,&#34;languageId&#34;:10,&#34;lastForumTopicId&#34;:123531132,&#34;lastForumTopicCreateDate&#34;:&#34;2025-12-29 09:01:43&#34;,&#34;lastUserId&#34;:416898281,&#34;topicUserId&#34;:1802156,&#34;bodyButtonSet&#34;:null,&#34;create_timestamp&#34;:1767027703,&#34;topicUsername&#34;:&#34;fr0z3nshad3&#34;,&#34;lastPostUserId&#34;:416898281,&#34;lastPostUsername&#34;:&#34;Barry_Muli&#34;,&#34;lastPostMembershipLevel&#34;:50,&#34;authorChessTitle&#34;:null,&#34;lastPostUserIsEnabled&#34;:true,&#34;lastPostUserIsContentHidden&#34;:false,&#34;lastPostUserUuid&#34;:&#34;5830c5e0-d019-11ef-bb5f-e1534cb1a352&#34;,&#34